name: Time Is Money......(literally)
description:
This game is for "Gamedev.tv Community Jam". Time is Money......(literally) is about running fast as sanic boi and collecting all the money within a given time limit. Plus you also get a meme button to click.

Game made by : BeepBeepLol69

Made In Godot Engine

Assets :

Luis Zino  - City Background 

Kenney - Player and the Tiles

Ethan's Pixel Art Shop - Portal

Havran - Money

Khurusan - Game's Font (Low Batt Font)

dafont.com - Banner and Timer Font (Candles Font)

Vapxiel - UI Banner

dklon - Jumping Sound

jalastram - Money and Button Hover Sound

Tim Beek - Main Menu and Credits Music

den_yes - Game Over Sound Effect

Eric Matyas - Game's Background Music

This is my third game and my first game to be uploaded on the internet. Feel free to criticize or suggest anything about the game.
